Will click in check box once. You need to set the value of 'Expected' on a 'Set' action to be the expected state AFTER the click. On a 'Get' you should set the value to something other than 'None'. 'Out Value' is a string, and will have one of the following values: 'Un-Selected', 'Selected', or 'Mixed'. If 'Hard Set' is used, up to two clicks will be generated to attempt to set check box to value chosen in 'Expected'.
